Kaelthiere is a terrible goddess of fire worshipped by Azer, efreet, salamanders, and other races, including humans, with an unhealthy interest in the dark side of fire. She is also known as the Dark Flame, the Consuming Flame, and the Devourer. Her favored weapon is the shortspear.
Other powers worshipped by the efreet include Kossuth, Imix, Agni, and Freya. 

